{"tid":1278554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重申］尋晚立法會有開記招！有讀宣言！","createTime":"2019-07-02T13:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T13:18:38.000Z","uid":66390,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b25db8148e614bbb84398e9bc7286cf1c1b5d487","tid":1278554,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"我想講：<br />\n尋晚睇live已經見到有朋友仔<br />\n開左記招 讀左宣言！<br />\n要播 就會播<br />\n我唔想再見到有post話要讀宣讀 個感覺好似話尋晚無讀咁<br />\n我想保護佢地<br />\n佢地盡哂力 去到最後一刻 警察都到左附近<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">都堅持要讀 讀完先走呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">讀左啦！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入面既人 都會聽大家講 讀左宣言</span><br />\n<br />\n我朋友仔比唔少一位記者抄左牌<br />\n大家想有咩說話想佢托記者講<br />\n歡迎大家留comments <br />\n佢會睇哂<br />\n<br />\n如果大家想再開記招 我都唔反對"},{"pid":"566f98afb48349669de57e2119ed5ae625992ddf","tid":1278554,"uid":66390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spAfr5y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspAfr5y.png&h=327babbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68H5Pi0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68H5Pi0.png&h=8506491c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iPNUHD1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiPNUHD1.png&h=94eda8ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19061d827d387dcf1547c9ec70c566e7c113ee08","tid":1278554,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:09:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">想尋日有出現既人 睇一睇</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［入來］社運需要進步！我有以下建議...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1278043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1278043</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bdc191bd8e5b59d8351b76c880c1fbe8f10847a1","tid":1278554,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"記招link <br />\n<br /